title: AVAILABLE NOW! Renovated 1x1 w/washer & dryer - Walkable Hyde Park
posting_body: ['The 407 is a charming boutique style community made up of spacious 1 bedroom homes.', 'This unique property is centrally located on E 38th st and Guadalupe st, conveniently located in the North University and Hyde Park Neighborhoods.', 'This newly renovated apartment is available immediately, and features wood floors throughout, 2 huge closets with built in shelving, quartz counters, stainless steel appliances, and in-unit washer/dryer!!!', 'VIRTUAL TOUR HERE: https://youtu.be/qcNF-Z7gAcU', 'We have no weight or breed restrictions for well behaved pets.', 'APPLICATION DETAILS:', '----------------------------------------------------------', '$75/applicant (adults over 18 years old)', '$150 Admin Fee', '$400 Deposit due at move in', '$250 Pet Fee', '$25/month Pet Rent']
